    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting at 1st level, your existence in a twilight state between life and death makes you difficult to defeat. When damage reduces you to 0 hit points, you can make a Charisma saving throw (DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">5</span> + the damage taken). On a success, you instead drop to 1 hit point. You can't use this feature if you are reduced to 0 hit points by radiant damage or by a critical hit.</p><p>After the saving throw succeeds, you can't use this feature again until you finish a long rest.</p></div>",
